```bash
nano flux-system.json

Locate the Finalizers Section: Look for a section that resembles this:
"finalizers": [
    "fluxcd.io/finalizer"
]

Remove or Modify the Finalizers: You can either delete the entire finalizers field or set it to an empty array:
"finalizers": []

Step 3: Apply the Modified JSON
Now that you have modified the JSON file, apply it to remove the finalizers:
Execute the Following Command:
kubectl replace --raw "/api/v1/namespaces/flux-system/finalize" -f ./flux-system.json

Verify:
kubectl get namespaces
